### WGC Backend API Examples

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@partnerApiKey = sample-partner-key-123

### 1. Register User (Partner Admin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@partner.com",
  "password": "securepassword123",
  "role": "partner_admin"
}

### 2. Login
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@partner.com",
  "password": "securepassword123"
}

### 3. Onboarding: Create Merchant (Requires Auth)
@token = {{login.response.body.token}}
POST {{baseUrl}}/onboarding/merchant
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "First Baptist Church",
  "email": "finance@fbc.org",
  "partnerId": "uuid-of-partner"
}

### 4. Payments: Process Donation (Via Partner API Key)
POST {{baseUrl}}/payments/donate
x-api-key: {{partnerApiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 100.00,
  "merchantId": "uuid-of-merchant",
  "donorName": "John Doe",
  "donorEmail": "john@example.com"
}

### 5. Dashboard Summary (Requires Partner Admin Auth)
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. Migration: Import Donors
POST {{baseUrl}}/migration/import
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "merchantId": "uuid-of-merchant",
  "donors": [
    { "email": "donor1@test.com", "name": "Donor One" },
    { "email": "donor2@test.com", "name": "Donor Two" }
  ]
}

### 7. Contact Form
POST {{baseUrl}}/contact
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Potential Partner",
  "email": "growth@softwareco.com",
  "message": "We would like to integrate WGC into our platform."
}

### 8. Webhook: Simulate Finix Event
POST {{baseUrl}}/webhooks/finix
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "payment.succeeded",
  "data": {
    "id": "pay_mock123",
    "amount": 5000,
    "tags": {
      "internal_payment_id": "uuid-of-internal-payment"
    }
  }
}
